  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Currently, the client will **automatically deposit 100ETH from the user's account** into the the VMC validator set. In the future, we need to allow users to specify whether or not they want to take this action, perhaps as a cli flag upon launching the sharding client.\r\n\r\n`geth shard --joinvalidatorset`\r\n\r\nwill deposit the 100ETH automatically into the VMC.\r\n\r\n`geth shard`\r\n\r\nwill start the client and **not** deposit the ETH automatically.",
